Entity.fast-splitter.locDescr: Splits and/or joins transport belts' cargo 1:1.

Entity.nuclear-reactor.locDescr: Uses uranium fuel cells to generate heat. The heat output increases when built next to other reactors.

Entity.rail-signal.locDescr: Defines the rail system into blocks, allowing multiple trains to run on the same network.

Entity.rail-chain-signal.locDescr: Reads the next signals in the path to allow better control of the trains.

Entity.radar.locDescr: Scans the nearby sectors, and actively reveals an area around it.

Entity.roboport.locDescr: Connects with other roboports to create the construction and logistic networks used by construction and logistic robots.

Entity.splitter.locDescr: Splits and/or joins transport belts' cargo 1:1.

Entity.rocket-silo.locDescr: Used to craft and launch a rocket to win the game.

Entity.solar-panel.locDescr: During daytime it produces 100% of the power output which drops to 0% at night.

Entity.heat-exchanger.locDescr: Uses heat energy to turn water into steam.

Entity.boiler.locDescr: Burns fuel to turn water into steam.

Entity.beacon.locDescr: Transmits the effect of modules to nearby friendly entities.

Entity.arithmetic-combinator.locDescr: Performs arithmetic operations on circuit network signals.

Entity.accumulator.locDescr: Stores a limited amount of energy when available production exceeds demand, and releases it in the opposite case.

Entity.big-ship-wreck-3.locDescr: A segment of the crashed ship.

Entity.big-ship-wreck-2.locDescr: A segment of the crashed ship.

Entity.big-ship-wreck-1.locDescr: A segment of the crashed ship.

Entity.crash-site-chest-2.locDescr: A container from the crashed ship. It might contain useful items.

Entity.crash-site-chest-1.locDescr: A container from the crashed ship. It might contain useful items.

Entity.construction-robot.locDescr: Automatically build and repair friendly entities.
